data.description: This 4 bedroom, 2 bath home rests in the quiet community of Jackson Glenn, and is within walking distance to the community pool and tennis courts. Sidewalks throughout make it a great place for walks. The private back yard brings a beautiful, seasonal view. Come sit on your back porch in your little oasis, while being minutes from the interstate for an easy commute to work, shopping, dining and much more. The living room offers a fireplace for cozy winter nights, and flows into the kitchen and back deck. You don't want to miss this great home. Schedule a showing today!
